# Public API base URL. EVERY request in this app is built as
# `${NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL}${path}` where path comes exclusively from
# src/lib/api/endpoints.ts. This must be exactly the host, no /api/v1
# suffix — endpoints.ts already includes the full /api/v1/... prefix
# per the literal strings in api_endpoints.txt.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.qalbconverfy.in